summary: I've been thinking a lot about this today so I wanna share. I think it hasn't really registered yet that the world of Dan and...
body: I’ve been thinking a lot about this today so I wanna share. I think it hasn’t really registered yet that the world of Dan and Phil is gonna change really soon… and not in a bad way. I remember them saying that this tour is most likely the last time they’ll be meeting fans in this kind of setting. They’ll probably stop attending playlist and vidcon too. We always talk about how eventually they’ll get a forever home and a dog and start their family and finally settle down. I think that’s closer than anyone realizes. Once tour is over they are gonna buy a house. They are gonna get a dog. They could actually get married. They might adopt a kid. These ideas we’ve had for so long are going to become reality. And while it might seem crazy to think about it’s actually realistic. Idk I’m just excited for the next chapter.
